hkobject.hkparam: Glide if ((Speed >= TargetSpeedDamped * TargetSpeedThresholdMin) && (Speed <= TargetSpeedDamped * TargetSpeedThresholdMax) && (!IsGliding) )
Speed = clamp(Speed - (MaxDec * TimeStep), min(Speed, TargetSpeedDamped), Speed)
Speed = clamp(Speed + (MaxAcc * TimeStep), Speed, max(Speed, TargetSpeedDamped * TargetSpeedMaxScale))
MaxSpeedDamped = MinSpeed + ( ( MaxSpeedCurrent - MinSpeed ) * ( PathAngleThreshold- clamp(PathAngle, 0, PathAngleThreshold) ) / PathAngleThreshold )
TweenSpeedDamped = cond( TweenSpeed < TweenSpeedMin, TweenSpeedMin, TweenSpeed )
PhonemeBlendTarget = cond ( ( LipBigAah > 0 ) || ( LipDST > 0 ) || ( LipEee > 0 ) || ( LipFV > 0 ) || ( LipK > 0 ) || ( LipL > 0 ) || ( LipR > 0 ) || ( LipTh > 0 ), 1 , 0 ) * !bWantCastVoice
PhonemeBlend = clamp( PhonemeBlend + LipAcc* TimeStep * (PhonemeBlendTarget - PhonemeBlend), 0, 1 )
fPhonemeDefaultWeight = cond( LipBigAahDamped || LipDSTDamped || LipEeeDamped || LipFVDamped || LipKDamped || LipLDamped || LipRDamped || LipThDamped, 0, 1 )
